PrecisORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (1999-No.4, Tombstone Territorial Park Reservation, Y.T.) - which prohibits, until December 31, 2002, the staking of mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on a particular tract of land in the Yukon Territory.
